title: Dark Angel - Children of the Revolution (A Fan Edit by Uncanny A
description:
Dark Angel - Children of the Revolution

A Fan Edit by Uncanny Antman



"I, like many DA fans, was none too impressed by a lot of season 2. I decided to distil the entire season into a story that I could watch and enjoy, without having to cringe at some pretty mediocre television.

The film is three hours and twenty minutes long. (Which includes a specially made, eight minute long recap of the season one finale.) 

Some of the episodes are used heavily, others not so much. (For example, I only used one scene from "Gill Girl" and from "Dawg Dog Afternoon", I literally only used a single shot.) 

I sincerely hope you all enjoy. For best viewing, try to forget everything you know about season 2, and don&#039;t let it influence what you expect of this edit. " 

~ Uncanny Antman
